ts/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係做到好足<br />\n趁你記憶猶新，講下有咩要做<br />\n當幫手溫習"},{"pid":"38f8da05ed57d51e634472379cfe0e1f2dc76709","tid":164890,"uid":24704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"上星期pass左  1take 多石 好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個日見到有巴打抽到大涌橋覺得佢好慘 等成績個陣聽到個個都係考多石但得佢一個大涌橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16df49ac651bd152aa1b06fd0ec48a51a46a725e","tid":164890,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上星期pass左  1take 多石 好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個日見到有巴打抽到大涌橋覺得佢好慘 等成績個陣聽到個個都係考多石但得佢一個大涌橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢就係要交數嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37aa72983f886787e0ca05921647395a8050e3b","tid":164890,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊條線</blockquote><br />\n多石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正<br />\n有冇咩覺得自己做得好？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得自己做足曬，而且無咩特別情況<br />\n一落車就知道合格左9成<br />\n好多謝巴士叔叔讓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後睇翻，6個輕微</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係做到好足<br />\n趁你記憶猶新，講下有咩要做<br />\n當幫手溫習</blockquote><br />\n我多石1 take 但21個輕微tick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5e2e5021797f9561d2d62d1749d838c27d9a21","tid":164890,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊條線</blockquote><br />\n多石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正<br />\n有冇咩覺得自己做得好？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得自己做足曬，而且無咩特別情況<br />\n一落車就知道合格左9成<br />\n好多謝巴士叔叔讓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後睇翻，6個輕微</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係做到好足<br />\n趁你記憶猶新，講下有咩要做<br />\n當幫手溫習</blockquote><br />\n最緊要路要熟，轉線考牌官唔會講，去到燈位先發現無轉就多數肥<br />\n望鏡擰頭呢d強逼自己要做足，一夠空就上三波，停車前先減速<br />\n好多野我諗你阿sir都成日講，我既tips係一定要熟路<br />\n平時學車阿sir會提埋你打燈轉線擰頭，有d位係直接轉完行右線，呢d野一到考試就要靠自己，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee89877872a27188bb63826f771f0e3d63fbe08","tid":164890,"uid":24704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"平時師父多數叫我綀多石多 好少行其他"},{"pid":"967af7216efd7e0fd56d48a2bc765983583d34ad","tid":164890,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上星期pass左  1take 多石 好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個日見到有巴打抽到大涌橋覺得佢好慘 等成績個陣聽到個個都係考多石但得佢一個大涌橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩無抽中我，真係驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實其他駕院會唔會有無得學既路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ed94190436bd7bad8e6d1d689f243eaeb856bc","tid":164890,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"河畔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c8680ee002d1a371d496ed4675a91239ad5c22","tid":164890,"uid":54927