kgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個知字都好</blockquote><br />\n越早越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n14:00 呢啲時間可唔可以俾條銀城我考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點未必有銀城考<br />\n唔太sure</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唉，狂煲啲路線先"},{"pid":"89340c0f38982c523c0ec30e29a6d87fa7ecdb1f","tid":164890,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時上開智專個師傅都話3波要暢順直路先好轉<br />\n岩先個堂咁岩係代課佢係咪都要我轉三波<br />\n甚至十個車位都叫我轉，埋到去先落二波<br />\n<br />\nfor考試係咪應該唔洗理成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我師傅都係瘋狂叫我用三波<br />\n十個車位我一定轉三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉得多用得好係好<br />\n但我覺得上左三波好快又落二波我唔夠信心可以夠時間拉得慢架車落二波<br />\n跟著就會chor"},{"pid":"dc6d759d225b1d3477a4c5c481bf0b216e886603","tid":164890,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"好撚驚 一陣沙駕上第一堂<br />\n第一堂係咪要渣出街?"},{"pid":"4512e9b3750c7fbf373ee9a4e73b74e1e06c4fb4","tid":164890,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚驚 一陣沙駕上第一堂<br />\n第一堂係咪要渣出街?</blockquote><br />\n我第一堂係場到兜圈<br />\n學車無乜好驚<br />\n有個師傅旁住你一定無事"},{"pid":"afd78ed2ceb71200947cc35c201013dca757bd53","tid":164890,"uid":62850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚驚 一陣沙駕上第一堂<br />\n第一堂係咪要渣出街?</blockquote><br />\n我第一堂係場到兜圈<br />\n學車無乜好驚<br />\n有個師傅旁住你一定無事</blockquote><br />\n前排唔係有個女人炒車炒到四輪朝天咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89efb3dc970a510083880e1f341042b6f3c973ba","tid":164890,"uid":8231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚驚 一陣沙駕上第一堂<br />\n第一堂係咪要渣出街?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n場內兜圈，師傅會睇下你程度決定幾時出街"},{"pid":"4e92fa10913327b084e17c86dad6a31c117baea6","tid":164890,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時上開智專個師傅都話3波要暢順直路先好轉<br />\n岩先個堂咁岩係代課佢係咪都要我轉三波<br />\n甚至十個車位都叫我轉，埋到去先落二波<br />\n<br />\nfor考試係咪應該唔洗理成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我師傅都係瘋狂叫我用三波<br />\n十個車位我一定轉三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉得多用得好係好<br />\n但我覺得上左三波好快又落二波我唔夠信心可以夠時間拉得慢架車落二波<br />\n跟著就會chor</blockquote><br />\n基本上學左一排都會知考嘅線路交通情況係點嫁啦，咩位上三波一定預得到"},{"pid":"af2720f9d29708a54833c680fbc7b9a82cd0ee39","tid":164890,"uid":32013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得最難應該係河畔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n河畔好L難 肥過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de158126e86cbd074256040a62fdedf4a243d181","tid":164890,"uid":6790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"恭喜曬樓主"},{"pid":"d6a22a0d7a411130655be213bb34a5e929df2015","tid":164890,"uid":16471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講沙駕可以睇考試時間估計邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個知字都好</blockquote><br />\n越早越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n14:00 呢啲時間可唔可以俾條銀城我考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點未必有銀城考<br />\n唔太sure</blockquote><br />\n關咩事呀 我三點都係銀城啦"},{"pid":"9b6cfa41a3db416ce11df6084b21cb6c9401c06c","tid":164890,"uid":19497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"29號考沙駕 好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9aa112815a5a58e1deea3ab589be603f95af2e","tid":164890,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講沙駕可以睇考試時間估計邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個知字都好</blockquote><br />\n越早越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n14:00 呢啲時間可唔可以俾條銀城我考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點未必有銀城考<br />\n唔太sure</blockquote><br />\n關咩事呀 我三點都係銀城啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你俾返啲希望我<br />\n仲有一個星期多啲<br />\n開始緊張喇"},{"pid":"52b3b096025723eb2169694ec152e73d1d22b74d","tid":164890,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>29號考沙駕 好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dea715a99363cfd48b7bc0670938671359e30a","tid":164890,"uid":8231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講沙駕可以睇考試時間估計邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個知字都好</blockquote><br />\n越早越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n14:00 呢啲時間可唔可以俾條銀城我考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點未必有銀城考<br />\n唔太sure</blockquote><br />\n關咩事呀 我三點都係銀城啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問過師傅，佢話<br />\n臨收工又有時間剩，就會揀條長既考<br />\n銀城/多石，多數上午食飯前考，因為趕放飯<br />\n又或者果日多考生做唔切，就會揀最短去考"},{"pid":"f0573a7bf4dd0e27db56515924cc48c093ec547c","tid":164890,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時上開智專個師傅都話3波要暢順直路先好轉<br />\n岩先個堂咁岩係代課佢係咪都要我轉三波<br />\n甚至十個車位都叫我轉，埋到去先落二波<br />\n<br />\nfor考試係咪應該唔洗理成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我師傅都係瘋狂叫我用三波<br />\n十個車位我一定轉三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉得多用得好係好<br />\n但我覺得上左三波好快又落二波我唔夠信心可以夠時間拉得慢架車落二波<br />\n跟著就會chor</blockquote><br />\n我三波轉二波都係chok，不過盡量chok少d，呢d位應該都係輕微姐<br />\n有位就轉三波，差唔多就轉翻二波順勢停<br />\n驚唔夠時間落二波就加腳制減速，好似係"},{"pid":"5e6d36d8eca56cc102f6aa2523b2a7bb0281d2b0","tid":164890,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恭喜曬樓主</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba436a4f0d63f37ff58bf1589501de456b8b9e8","tid":164890,"uid":63905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講沙駕可以睇考試時間估計邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個知字都好</blockquote><br />\n越早越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n14:00 呢啲時間可唔可以俾條銀城我考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前14:00係多石"},{"pid":"2e97b389203fd220259a76ba80e81161e2980f00","tid":164890,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講沙駕可以睇考試時間估計邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個知字都好</blockquote><br />\n越早越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上個月9:35考大涌橋肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc1b33a4f18e00cfa5009889a8a63b456a429f4","tid":164890,"uid":54783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"第一堂就出街<br />\n超速衝燈尾閘其他學神頭都做均晒<br />\n個師傅仲問我以前係咪揸過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13198e2bd6eec0105b9c701d119c80972aea1974","tid":164890,"uid":11672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一堂就出街<br />\n超速衝燈尾閘其他學神頭都做均晒<br />\n個師傅仲問我以前係咪揸過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一堂出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431e238faf3753a3371062fd2d84042c82ee649a","tid":164890,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講沙駕可以睇考試時間估計邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s